<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.3.7">
<l>cumantu māmalar nīrcuṭar tūpaṅkoṇ</l>
<l>ṭāmarntu vāṉavar vāṉavar kōṉoṭu</l>
<l>namaṉṟe ḻuntiru vēṅkaṭan naṅkaṭku</l>
<l>camaṉkoḷ vīṭu taruntaṭaṅ kuṉṟamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Sacred Vēṅkaṭam where suitably rise in obeissance</l> 
<l>the celestials and the king of the celestials</l>
<l>laden with big flowers, water, lamps [and] incense,</l>
<l>is the broad hill that gives peaceful liberation to us.</l>

      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
